reviewText: It's been good so far until tonight in season 5 were the disc started messing up. Still love it though,can you get a refund?
The dvds themselves are great no problems at all, however the envelope in which they arrived was completely torn open at the top as if it had been tampered with
Awesome, received quickly in the mail!  Im hooked for life now.....

It took me six seasons to finally watch an episode. Wow! Did I ever get hooked! The writers of this series are phenomenal! They present and deal with many human nature encounters. Now on Sunday nights I am glued to AMC.
the recipient was thrilled she did not know books like this were available
